  "instructions": [
    "In a large clay pot, heat the sesame oil over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add the gochujang sauce and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the brown sugar, fish sauce, soy sauce, and Korean chili flakes. Cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the shrimp and cook for 2-3 minutes per side, until they are pink and cooked through.",
    "Add the water and bring to a simmer.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cook for 5-7 minutes, or until the sauce has thickened slightly.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Garnish with sliced green onions and serve immediately"
  ],
